readable.content: A girl is standing on a graffiti covered stone with something in her mouth . A girl is standing on a painted slab of cement and twisting her body to look up at the camera . A girl poses for the camera , with her mouth open and a yellow stick coming out of it . A girl stands on a graffitied wall , her head skewed sideways . The girl in the jacket is on the cement with a sucker in her mouth and a bike to the right .
